Edit Attributes Transformation: Change the Column Names and Value Formats
In a Transform node of a Data Prep recipe, select the column in the Preview tab.
In the Transform toolbar, click the Edit Attributes button ().
Change the column attributes:
- Label: The display label for the column.
- API Name: The API name of the column.
- Precision: The maximum number of digits in a numeric column.
- Scale: The number of digits to the right of the decimal point in a numeric column.
- Length: The maximum number of characters in a text column.
- Date Format: The date format of a date column.
